➜沃尔沃将打造全尺寸SUV，双排座椅布局，XC100了解一下
http://www.sohu.com/a/429234270_99994080	35030
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201103/3c86c275504e4912bae656be28ae4a7e.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
